        <li><strong>Comparative tables</strong> by region, RAL amount, monthly net salary and other tax variables</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        All services are offered free of charge and without registration. The Website does not require account creation, does not have restricted areas and does not offer paid services.
      </p>

